ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
SubjectCanada-Prince Edward Island Immigration Agreement
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration to ENTER INTO a CANADA-PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND IMMIGRATION AGREEMENT with the Government of PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND in order to define their respective roles and responsibilities with respect to immigration, specifically in the case of the Provincial Nominee Program, and to ensure that they reflect the program authorities under the Immigration and Refugee Protection Act.
